Package gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.binding.metapath.item

Interface IXdmFactory

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefaultXdmFactory
    public interface IXdmFactory
    This factory interface provides methods to create new INodeItem instances based on Metaschema information. These node items represent a node graph of parsed data that can be queried using a Metapath expression.

        Generate a new document node item.
        Parameters:
        definition - the Metaschema assembly definition that describes the model at the root of the document
        value - the bound object representing the data at the root of the document
        documentUri - the URI that was the source of the document, which is used for resolving relative URIs within the document
        Returns:
        a new document node item representing the rooted assembly value
